    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a reliable daily driver. While the engine and transmission are in good working order and the car performs well on the road, it does show signs of its age. You can expect some cosmetic wear on the exterior and interior, along with minor mechanical items that may require attention in the future. Overall, it is a solid, functional car for a budget-conscious buyer looking for utility over perfection.",
