    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable vehicle at an incredible value? This car is in fair condition and ready to get you where you need to go! It shows some honest signs of use and character from its time on the road, but it remains a functional and hardworking choice for anyone seeking affordable transportation. Don't miss out on this practical ride!",
