    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This unit has been thoroughly inspected to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for roadworthiness and driver comfort. Offering a balanced synthesis of performance and value, this vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a reliable, high-caliber automotive investment. Experience the assurance of a vehicle that has been preserved with professional care.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
